{"tid":2237282,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中國研究：「手機」一詞的確最早於大陸流行","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T10:59:16.000Z","uid":80481,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"64e7b17dd6b0d855b0dce137bc06194ccabdf6a8","tid":2237282,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:29:11.000Z","msg":"《從「手機」看不同華語社區同義詞群的競爭與選擇》<br />\n作者：邵敬敏 劉杰（暨南大學中文系）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyS4Xhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyS4Xhk.png&h=effd06cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.ixueshu.com/document/76f97d73a7da5c18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ixueshu.com%2Fdocument%2F76f97d73a7da5c18.html&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=2820c8b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ixueshu.com/document/76f97d73a7da5c18.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYzSmLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYzSmLu.png&h=a8241ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psMJtqx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpsMJtqx.png&h=389690ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f70d2e659ba1b6db8116e050fe3bf4bc9fa2b711","tid":2237282,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"1996年11月21日 《人民日報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lc1dQE2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc1dQE2.png&h=9aec0c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.laoziliao.net/rmrb/1996-11-21-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.laoziliao.net%2Frmrb%2F1996-11-21-7&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c1d3320a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.laoziliao.net/rmrb/1996-11-21-7</a>"},{"pid":"ca72fcd2669f119c18f5c3e6850d9c6d37224ce5","tid":2237282,"uid":22898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,